Refresh information every 5 seconds:
.B glances
\-t 5
.PP
.SH EXIT STATUS
Glances returns a zero exit status if it succeeds to print/grab information.
.PP
It returns 2 if it fails to parse its options (missing arguments, invalid value, etc).
